sc.model

Class OperationModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • sc.model.OperationModel
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ComputeModel

    public abstract class OperationModel
extends java.lang.Object
    OperationModel is an abstract class which define the model of SimpleCount application

    The model stores data that is retrieved according to commands from the controller and displayed in the view.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    bechad_p
